        "paragraph_index": 1,
        "text": "Notes\n- SRD‑46 links this record to many papers. Among those, the earliest primary publication cited for the Cu–EDTA constant is the 1949 Helv. Chim. Acta paper by Ackermann and Schwarzenbach. Additional primary reports (also linked to the same VLM record) include G. Schwarzenbach and E. Freitag, Helv. Chim. Acta, 1951, 34, 1503.\n- If you’d like me to pinpoint exactly which of these the curator used for the 18.78 value, I can follow up with deeper linkage tracing.",
